<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西飞过西街。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿在干什么？”一个男人喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在追赶谁吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么也没看见。”另一个人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！一个邮箱被炸毁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信件飞得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！她再一次用眼睛发射激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次一个垃圾箱被炸毁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿在毁灭美罗城！”一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她看起来很生气！”一个孩子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落地以后看看四周，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后用力跺了一下脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是最精彩的一集！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们正在杰克家看《大力士》。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望大力士能阻止那只蜥蜴怪兽！”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“大力士肯定能阻止怪兽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是超级英雄嘛！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一则新闻报道出现在电视屏幕上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有一条重大新闻。”记者说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上，有人看到火箭女孩儿正在毁灭美罗城。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿绝对不会那样做！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>记者继续报道。“一名目击者录下了整个过程。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>录像显示，火箭女孩儿正在毁灭东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正如大家看到的，她看起来非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人知道她为什么那么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>MBS新闻将会持续报道这一事件！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我们回到《大力士》。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>画面回到《大力士》，但是罗西和朋友们已经不想看了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿不可能毁灭美罗城。”特勒尔说，“我不相信！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克耸耸肩。“新闻都播出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔想了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许她正在追赶一个坏人。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉摇摇头。“录像里没有别人啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔摸着下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，也许那个坏人速度太快了，我们看不见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个比火箭女孩儿还快的坏人？”玛拉说，“不可能！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看起来非常不高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没事儿吧，罗西？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃......啊？我？哦，我还好。怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么看待火箭女孩儿的行为呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不会觉得她是一个坏人吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，火箭女孩儿的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去去就回来。”罗西说，“我要喝点水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走进杰克家的厨房后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>按下了手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们差点儿就抓到了幽灵强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他刚才打算抢劫美罗城造币厂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察已经把大楼包围了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们到处都找不到他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。”罗西说，“我马上就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>